# Input

```vue
<div v-for=' item      of   items '>{{ item }}</div>
<div v-for="item     of    items">{{ item }}</div>
<div v-for='( value , key )     of object'>{{ key }}: {{ value }}</div>

```


# Formatted

```vue
<div v-for='item of items'>{{ item }}</div>
<div v-for="item of items">{{ item }}</div>
<div v-for='(value, key) of object'>{{ key }}: {{ value }}</div>

```
